bio.info: A tamoan chihuahua who is usually very nice and active, but can be overconfident and cocky at times. He has yellow-orange fur, green shoes, and a blue collar. He is mostly clueless about the world around him, but he would really like to explore it more and make friends along the way.
bio.backstory: Sparky's from Planet Tamoa. He has been living in his hometown for 11 years. It has been very peaceful and happy in that hometown, until it was attacked and war broke out. The president of the town instructed the youth to evacuate the planet to a partner planet via an emergency space ship. Sparky's trip was going fine, until the space ship started going out of his control and went crazy, and ended up crashing on the only place in the rp atm L. He was seriously injured from the crash but was able to recover. The events still come in his mind at times, but he stays calm and acts like it never happened most of the time.

bio.info: A cheerful Tanuki and somewhat egotistical, and has perfectionist tendencies. He wears a slightly loose, blue short-sleeved turtleneck to match his Brown fur with dark tan cargo shorts. And a utility belt where he keeps his shortsword around his waist. He may resemble Spectra in many ways, both being Tanukis, but Sky's tail is slightly larger, as well as being a bit fluffier.
bio.backstory: As a traveling warrior, he's seen many places and people. Through these travels, he has gained battle experience by simply mimicking what others do. Sometimes you can spot him with a leaf on his head. Being a Tanuki, he gets rather lonely, as there is almost no fellow Tanuki in the world. Spectra is the only exception to this, but as she came from a different planet, it's a bit awkward for him to approach her.
